CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 18, 1954, pg. 10 reads: "Guild Luncheon Participants - When the Urban League Guild gave its luncheon last Thursday noon at the Fort Pitt Hotel, the trio of charming ladies shown above, took part in program. Left to right: Mollie Moon, founder of the Guild; Mrs. victor Shaw, guest speaker, and Mrs. Robert L. Vann, who presided. - Garland Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mollie Moon, Mrs. Victor Shaw, and Jessie Vann gathered in Fort Pitt Hotel for Urban League luncheon
